      "message": "Line 443: `selectFirst_` is used with `.exchange(false)` implying it is `std::atomic\u003cbool\u003e`, but `setFilter({})` and other members are called from the lambda which may run on a different thread than the QObject\u0027s thread. `QTimer::singleShot` dispatches to `this`\u0027s thread, so this is likely safe, but the comment should note the threading assumption. Also, a 1-second timeout is short on slow connections and may hide valid late results.",
